comments[2]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-24T06:30:12.221Z",claude-code-agent,"Duplicate check: searched all statuses for PM-CLI-2K and the exact Schema migration migrationId must be non-empty signature. No canonical item exists; related schema-evolution and Sentry-classification lineages are linked."
  "2026-07-24T06:36:36.300Z",claude-code-agent,"Implementation evidence: schema rename/remap commands now fail at CLI preflight with code schema_migration_input_required, exit 2, compact missing-field recovery, and no raw TypeError. The SDK remains strict. A real temporary tracker confirmed a missing --migration-id returns the typed JSON envelope."
